segments.title: ManagedNotebookService registerInstance Sample
segments.description: Registers an existing legacy notebook instance to the Notebooks API server. Legacy instances are instances created with the legacy Compute Engine calls. They are not manageable by the Notebooks API out of the box. This call makes these instances manageable by the Notebooks API.
